 CreateQuestBJ(bj_QUESTTYPE_REQ_DISCOVERED,"Map","Your   is to defend  fortress  other players and be the  survivor. 
Usefull commands: -afk/-back, -mode"," ")
 CreateQuestBJ(bj_QUESTTYPE_REQ_DISCOVERED,"Game Modes","Random - Random pick, All options ON 
All Pick - All pick, All options ON 
Old Random - Random pick, Neutral Buildings OFF 
Old All Pick - All pick, Neutral Buildings OFF 
Minimal - All Pick, Neutral Buildings OFF, Special Bonuses OFF 
Noob - All pick, Neutral Buildings ON, Ultimate Weapons OFF, Stronger Barracks, Increased  picking time"," ")
 CreateQuestBJ(bj_QUESTTYPE_REQ_DISCOVERED,"Map Creator","This map (ispired by Chaos Control of IceHeart) was  entirely  by one person - Don Schneider  Lithuania. 
(EuroBattle.net nics: Sur5al, Zjb) 
(website: www.w3sur5al.com) 
(email: Schneide84@yahoo.co.uk) 
-New models  downloaded  Hiveworkshop. Sorry, but i am too  to  for people who   and   credit here. 
-I don't  models, but i  skins and icons."," ")
 CreateQuestBJ(bj_QUESTTYPE_OPT_DISCOVERED,"VI","I wrote triggers for Virtual Intelligence (there is no  thing as AI, not yet at least) so it is possible to   map  computer opponents. Choosing easy, normal or insane affects the amount of   get but not their actual behaviour. You can choose VI races, but you  to be Orange player to do that. Write the direction of the player -u, -r, -d, -l (up, right, down, left) and the number of the race. (-u1, -r5, -d9, -l11 are valid) 
Race numbers: 
1 - Human 
2 - Dwarf 
3 - Rogue 
4 - Orc 
5 - Troll 
6 - Tauren 
7 - Demon 
